Package: CCIcompass
Type: Package
Title: Composite Interaction Score (CIS) metric to rank cell-cell interactions (CCIs) across multiple inference tools.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Olha", "Kholod", , "olha.kholod@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: CIS based on ranked-biased precision (RBP), which prioritizes top-ranked interactions from methods implemented in LIANA package and calculates a weighted composite score that reflects agreement across tools, while accounting for rank position.
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    Seurat,
    liana,
    dplyr,
    readr,
    magrittr,
    tibble
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
